filtering sentences of the simplified text based on the entailment score to obtain a modified text;
computing a first hallucination score based on the complex text and the simplified text;
computing a second hallucination score based on the complex text and the modified text;
comparing the first hallucination score to the second hallucination score; and
providing the modified text as an output based on the comparison.

16. An apparatus for language processing, comprising:
